descriptionHtml:
Lullaai is the app that guides you night by night to improve the sleep of your baby. A sleep tracker will help your baby to sleep peacefully thanks to relaxing sounds and lullabies.

Lullaai creates a 15 nights custom plan for your baby that will help him to sleep all night thanks to our sound routines and the Perfect Night mode.
The Perfect Night mode calms your baby with lullabies, nature sounds and white noise. Also, if your baby wakes up, it will automatically reply with white noise to help him sleep and to calm him.

◉ HOW DOES LULLAAI WORK?

Our artificial intelligence tracks and recognizes your baby’s sleep phases and creates relaxing sounds that adapt to this moment to improve its rest thanks to lullabies, nature sounds and white noise designed especially by experts to help your baby relax during the routine and sleep better at night.

Forget about making notes of the sleep hours. Lullaai automatically follows up on the sleep so that you can see all the gathered data without needing to do it manually and thus have nights when you don’t have to wake up neither for your baby nor for you.

Once you register in the app, we will provide you with recommendations and content that will help, based on the age and behaviour of your baby.
You will be able to create healthy sleep habits for your baby. We have an article and video library for you to understand and learn everything about your baby’s sleep.

Sleep alerts. Lullaai will let you know when is the best time to start with the sleep routine with lullabies, nature sounds and white noise.

◉ LULLAAI, THE BABY SLEEP TRACKER, BY YOUR SIDE

SLEEP ADVISORS
Program your custom sleep plan or personal advising with one of our professional coaches. We will work together to make your baby have healthy sleep habits and get results as soon as possible.

Also, with Lullaai’s guarantee, if after the first advising you don’t want to go on with the process or you don’t get the expected results from the personal advising, we will refund the complete price.

Download the app and get to reconcile your baby’s sleep with Lullaai.

◉ HOW DOES LULLAAI’S METHOD WORK?

Lullaai’s method was created with the consent of pediatricians, psychologists and experts in baby’s sleep. Teaching healthy sleep habits to your baby improves its cognitive abilities, its development and its wellness. We based our method on studies about the baby’s sleep and the experience of our baby sleep coaches.

We want parents to be experts in their baby’s sleep for them to make their own decisions on the best way to improve their baby’s sleep. Besides, Lullaai’s app helps you with sleep routine, lullabies, nature sounds and white noises that help your baby relax and get a better sleep.

Lullaai is what you need to help your baby sleep better, make bedtime easier and reduce night wakings. Using a Baby Sleep Coach’s personalised counselling, sound routines, the Perfect Night Mode and science articles, Lullaai guides you along the path to understand and improve your baby’s sleep. • Lullabies and Sounds specifically designed to relax your baby.
• Content created by baby sleep specialists and reviewed by paediatricians.

Lullaai is the app to assist you with your baby’s sleep, help reduce wakings and make bedtime easier. Lullaai has been created by baby sleep experts and its content is reviewed by paediatricians and specialists.

How does the Lullaai app work?
• Chat unlimitedly with a Baby Sleep Coach, who will help you out with a sleep plan and answer all your specific queries.
